**Canonical:** @SnowSnake/flake.nix when in workspace (python + uv + platform libs + idempotent shellHook). Otherwise search for `pkgs.uv` in flake. Use nixos-mcp for `python313`, `uv`, `mkShell`.

**Responsibility matrix:** Python packages → uv (`pyproject.toml`). Interpreter + system libs → Nix (`flake.nix`). Virtualenv → uv (`.venv/` gitignored).

**Shell hook:** Idempotent — `if [ ! -d .venv ]; then uv sync; fi` then `source .venv/bin/activate`.
